“The heavens declare the glory of Yah, and the skies proclaim the work of His hands.” — Psalm 19:1


### 1. Quantum Mechanics Validates Faith
–**Double–slit experiment**: Reality changes when observed. Consciousness collapses probability into form.
–**Quantum entanglement**: Particles influence one another across space instantly — echoing omnipresence.
–**Observer effect**: Thought and attention shape what is real. Just as faith moves mountains, observation changes outcome.


