–Earth pulses at 7.83 Hz — the same as relaxed alpha waves in the human brain.
–We are tuned to Earth’s frequency. Electromagnetic storms change behavior, emotion, and thought.
–This proves the physical and spiritual are interwoven by design.


### 5. The Human Body Is an Antenna
–The heart’s electromagnetic field extends 10–15 feet from the body.
–The heart’s frequency dominates the body’s energy field.
–You don’t just exist — you radiate. You broadcast emotion, thought, and presence.


