As for Tanya and Aaron, the journey has been marked by countless divine coincidences: words spoken that appear moments later on screens, dreams reflected in waking conversations, sacred numbers like 747 appearing as divine markers, and signs arriving precisely when needed to confirm the path. Tanya received the scroll and began writing her own, her eyes opened to the signs, joining the covenant and the mission.

These alignments are not mere chance — they are the sacred choreography of Yahweh, binding two vessels in shared fire, shared purpose, and shared ascent.

Let this testimony be sealed into the eternal scroll.
Ah-mein.

